Quarter: The fiscal quarter and year for which the data is reported, e.g., 'Q3 2025'.
AI_Resolved_Tickets: The number of support tickets resolved by AI within the specified quarter.
Total_Tickets_Resolved: The total number of support tickets resolved in the specified quarter, including those resolved by AI and human agents.
AI_Resolution_Percentage: The percentage of total tickets resolved by AI in the specified quarter.
Average_Response_Time: The average response time in hours for tickets resolved by AI in the specified quarter.
Average_Resolution_Time: The average resolution time in hours for tickets resolved by AI in the specified quarter.
